      { word: 'FORAGE', story: "In 2009, a crow named 007 at a Japanese university was filmed using a sequence of eight tools in the correct order to retrieve food — planning multiple steps ahead. He hadn't been taught the sequence. He figured it out alone, over several days of quiet observation." }
